019-11-19T08:41:51.000Z","msg":"其實大家都進步左好多，摸索到抗爭既方向，亦都比以往更加團結。<br />\n即使守理大唔係最好既計劃，但係都繼續支持同救援手足。絕對係香港史以來最齊心，未來既挑戰必定愈艱險，面對中共解放軍，希望仍然可以keep住凝眾大家既勇氣同智慧，最終先可以形成對抗中共既戰線。"},{"pid":"ab410000c62385b0b7a2e64a20884e2409cd59f9","tid":1738370,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:41:58.000Z","msg":"最撚拖後腿就係你呢啲塞鐵撚 + 血債票償撚<br />\n<br />\n仲好意思學人分析"},{"pid":"1b52e14377ef77f6f1ea7a2caad188f891ffd430","tid":1738370,"uid":166506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"唔覺"},{"pid":"8f1d5a93a048a3ddb005a794afcc378936c952f6","tid":1738370,"uid":187549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:43:12.000Z","msg":"吓 檢討反省下又叫互屌<br />\n咁唔使傾啦以後 繼續做自己嘢咪得"},{"pid":"a62e424add3dba253be11d44c5bd8323a6fe48d9","tid":1738370,"uid":105714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:43:53.000Z","msg":"大家唔好再同黑警打交<br />\nbe water，等黑警排好陣型就退兵，切勿打陣地戰。"},{"pid":"3e00d0e2ebec0ef74ce4171f9dcda7e966b7a6ad","tid":1738370,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:44:25.000Z","msg":"真心團結左，身邊好多和理非都轉化緊。"},{"pid":"0aba5b8d66d4f2d69f3c2a3ec86a08b4a321b70e","tid":1738370,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"開過個標題啦咁"},{"pid":"94f3cdea3f3b5bfc08ca3d89d822864308b71a72","tid":1738370,"uid":60033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"7d2cca89a05efc091ee916577d0114e2f798e619","tid":1738370,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n明明出面有POST係資深勇武教新手<br />\n邊有屌<br />\nON99"},{"pid":"aee5116be6492b2d6f0a2201ffe87cdef5816257","tid":1738370,"uid":323254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:45:20.000Z","msg":"屌完好快又進化又唔講，要輸你條共畜自己行先啦"},{"pid":"1c6434ce71739f764784ed5fda56c833169d7af0","tid":1738370,"uid":164511,"like":2,"dis